  m_text: "\u201COnce there was a small bird named Binu. Binu was afraid to fly.
    One day, a strong wind lifted him into the sky. At first he was scared, but then
    he felt free and happy. From that day, Binu learned that trying new things can
    be exciting. At first he was scared, but then he felt free and happy.\u201D"
